<div id="pf55" class="pf wa hb" data-page-no="55"><div class="pc pc55 wa hb"><div class="t m689 xd5 h16 yad1 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON 11 September 7-13 </div><div class="t m53a x3 h2f yad2 ff1 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">E </div><div class="t m2f x3d h2f yad2 ff1 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t m60a x36 h3b yad2 ff2 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ith2 0</div><div class="t m7ed x90 h3b yad2 ff2 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">-</div><div class="t m7ee x58 h3b yad2 ff2 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">02E[lear </div><div class="t m4f5 x23 h16 y3d0 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Is any sick among you? let him call </div><div class="t m717 x51 h16 y73e ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">for the elders of the church; and let </div><div class="t m401 x51 h16 y73f ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">them pray over him, anointing him </div><div class="t m450 x51 h16 y740 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">with oil in the name of the Lord: and </div><div class="t m2d3 x51 h16 yad3 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the prayer of faith shall save the sick, </div><div class="t m1f5 x51 h16 yad4 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and the Lord shall raise him up; and if </div><div class="t m246 x51 h16 yad5 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">he have committed sins, they shall be </div><div class="t m2d8 x51 h16 ya15 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">forgiven him. Confess your faults one </div><div class="t m7ef x51 h16 yad6 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to another, and pray one for another, </div><div class="t mc3 x51 h16 ya17 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">that ye may be healed. The effectual </div><div class="t m7f0 x51 h16 ya18 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">fervent prayer of a righteous man </div><div class="t m7f1 x51 h16 ya19 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">availeth much&quot; (James 5:14-16). </div><div class="t m565 xd9 h14 yad7 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">One of Job&apos;s major problems was </div><div class="t m6cb x52 h14 yad8 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">physical illness. The record says, </div><div class="t m381 x51 h14 ya1d ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Satan left the Lord&apos;s presence and </div><div class="t m54b x51 h14 y32 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">made sores break out all over Job&apos;s </div><div class="t m7f2 x52 h14 ya1e ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">body&quot; (Job 2:7, TEV). Job refers to his </div><div class="t m7f3 x52 h14 ya1f ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">physical suffering in chapter 7, verses </div><div class="t m537 x51 h14 yad9 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3 through 5: </div><div class="t m7f4 xd9 h14 ya20 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Month after month I have nothing </div><div class="t m7f5 xcf h14 ya21 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to live for; </div><div class="t m47d xd6 h14 yada ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">night after night brings me grief. </div><div class="t m736 xd9 h14 ya22 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">When I lie down to sleep, the hours </div><div class="t m3aa xc8 h14 yadb ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">drag; </div><div class="t m7f6 xd6 h14 yadc ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">I toss all night and long for dawn. </div><div class="t m7f7 xd9 h14 ya25 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">My body is full of worms; </div><div class="t m65a xd6 h14 ya26 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">it is covered with scabs; </div><div class="t m39b xd6 h14 yadd ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">pus runs out of my sores&quot; (TEV). </div><div class="t m7f8 x8e h14 y3eb ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">And again, &apos; At night my bones all </div><div class="t m48c x8f h14 y3d1 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ache; the pain that gnaws me never </div><div class="t mf9 x8f h14 yade ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">stops&quot; (Job 30:17, TEV). </div><div class="t m490 x8e h14 y94e ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Job was one of millions who have </div><div class="t m590 x90 h14 y3d3 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">suffered physical pain. The alleviation </div><div class="t m27b x8f h14 y3d4 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of human suffering has become a </div><div class="t m26f x8f h14 y3d5 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">gigantic enterprise. Yet suffering </div><div class="t m7f9 x8f h14 yadf ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">continues to make life hard for the </div><div class="t m287 x90 h14 y3d6 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">human race. </div><div class="t m571 x8e h14 yae0 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The ministry of Jesus brought hope </div><div class="t m7fa x90 h14 yae1 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">for the sufferer. One of His main </div><div class="t m7fb x8f h14 y3d9 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">activities was the healing of the sick. </div><div class="t m7fc x8f h14 yae2 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Whithersoever he entered, into </div><div class="t m7fd x90 h14 yae3 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">villages, or cities, or country, they laid </div><div class="t m3ab x90 h14 y744 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the sick in the streets, and besought </div><div class="t m6b3 x90 h14 y745 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">him that they might touch if it were but </div><div class="t m7fe x90 h14 yae4 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the border of his garment: and as </div><div class="t m264 x90 h14 yae5 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">many as touched him were made </div><div class="t m475 x90 h14 y950 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">whole&quot; (Mark 6:56). </div><div class="t m7ff x58 h14 y747 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The apostles of Jesus received </div><div class="t m800 x90 h14 yae6 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">power to continue this healing </div><div class="t m801 x90 h14 y3f4 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ministry, and it became an important </div><div class="t m802 x90 h14 y748 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">function of the early church. It is listed </div><div class="t m803 x90 h14 y3f6 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">as one of the gifts of the Spirit. </div><div class="t m804 x58 h14 y749 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">In our present day, much is said </div><div class="t m7ac x90 h14 yae7 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">about &quot;faith healing.&quot; Popular books </div><div class="t m805 x90 h14 yae8 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">by faith healers recount story after </div><div class="t m806 x90 h14 yae9 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">story of successful healings. Other </div><div class="t m804 x90 h14 y3fa ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">observersjpoint to a much larger </div><div class="t m477 x90 h14 yaea ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">number of attempted but </div><div class="t m289 x90 h14 yaeb ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">unsuccessful &quot;cures.&quot; </div><div class="t m791 x58 h14 y74c ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The purpose of this lesson is to </div><div class="t m807 x90 h14 y3fd ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">survey the concept of divine </div><div class="t m808 x90 h14 yaec ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">healing—or faith healing as it is often </div><div class="t m4b6 x90 h14 yaed ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">called—and to endeavor to come to an </div><div class="t m809 x90 h14 yaee ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">understanding of this subject that will </div><div class="t m422 x90 h14 yaef ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">be useful to Christians in our day. </div><div class="t m65 x90 h16 y84 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">DAILY HIGHLIGHTS </div><div class="t m63 x90 h16 yaf0 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t m5a8 x91 h16 y403 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God&apos;s Investment in Man </div><div class="t m80a x91 h16 y959 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Gen. 1:26; 2:7) </div><div class="t m65 x90 h16 yaf1 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m401 x91 h16 yaf2 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God&apos;s Desire to Heal </div><div class="t m1ea x91 h16 y95a ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(1 Cor. 12:28) </div><div class="t m67 x90 h16 yaf3 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m5f7 x91 h16 y754 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Faith and Healing </div><div class="t m80b x91 h16 y755 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(James 5:15) </div><div class="t m69 x90 h16 yaf4 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t m83 x91 h16 yaf5 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Love and Healing </div><div class="t m120 x91 h16 y95c ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Matt. 20:30-34) </div><div class="t m6b x90 h16 yaf6 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="t m7cd x91 h16 yaf7 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Goodness and Healing </div><div class="t m80b x91 h16 yaf8 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(James 5:16) </div><div class="t m6d x90 h16 y559 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. </div><div class="t me4 x91 h16 yaf9 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">A Gift of the Spirit </div><div class="t m7df x91 h16 yafa ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(1 Cor. 12:4, 8, 9) </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
